\"addressLocality\":\"Norfolk\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":4,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/go-grooming-gallery-spa-and-training-llc\",\"name\":\"Go Grooming Gallery Spa and Training LLC.\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/go-grooming-gallery-spa-and-training-llc\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Go Grooming Gallery Spa and Training LLC..  What makes this dog facility special is its convenient, safe, excellent. convenient location with good parking Located...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Norfolk\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":5,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/k9-and-feline-daycare-services-llc\",\"name\":\"K9 and Feline Daycare Services, LLC\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/k9-and-feline-daycare-services-llc\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about K9 and Feline Daycare Services, LLC.  What makes this dog facility special is its attentive, knowledgeable, excellent. The staff's dedication to creating a positive...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Norfolk\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":6,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/kingdom-for-dogs\",\"name\":\"Kingdom For Dogs\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/kingdom-for-dogs\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Kingdom For Dogs.  What makes this dog facility special is its professional, reliable, attentive. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Norfolk\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":7,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/pawsnickety-pets\",\"name\":\"Pawsnickety Pets\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/pawsnickety-pets\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Pawsnickety Pets.  What makes this dog facility special is its excellent, friendly, caring. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Norfolk\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":8,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/petsmart-dog-training\",\"name\":\"PetSmart Dog Training\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/petsmart-dog-training\",\"description\":\"PetSmart Dog Training has become a favorite among the area residents.  What makes this dog facility special is its attentive, knowledgeable, spacious. The staff's dedication to creating a positive...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Norfolk\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":9,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/9-tails-pet-grooming-salon\",\"name\":\"9 Tails Pet Grooming salon\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/9-tails-pet-grooming-salon\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about 9 Tails Pet Grooming salon.  What makes this dog facility special is its spacious, clean, safe. spacious indoor play areas Located in a safe area, This facility...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Norfolk\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":10,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/bayview-pet-salon\",\"name\":\"Bayview Pet Salon\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/bayview-pet-salon\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Bayview Pet Salon.  What makes this dog facility special is its clean, friendly, caring. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Norfolk\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are dogs allowed on beaches in Norfolk, VA?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes—leashed dogs are welcome on all 7.3 miles of Norfolk’s public beaches, including Ocean View and Willoughby Spit, during the off-season (Labor Day through Memorial Day). During the summer season, pets are restricted to before 10 AM and after 6 PM to ensure safety during peak swimming hours.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I take my dog on the Elizabeth River Ferry?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Absolutely. Hampton Roads Transit (HRT) allows leashed dogs on the Elizabeth River Ferry, which connects downtown Norfolk to Olde Towne Portsmouth. It’s a unique, pet-friendly way to commute across the water while enjoying skyline views.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the main dog licensing rules in Norfolk?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"All dogs over 4 months old must be licensed with the City of Norfolk and have proof of rabies vaccination. Licenses are $10 for spayed/neutered pets and $15 otherwise. Note that the city also has a specific ordinance limiting households to no more than four dogs.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Which parks in Norfolk offer the most shade?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Bea McLoughlin Dog Park in Ghent is a local favorite specifically for its heavy tree canopy, providing essential relief during Virginia’s humid summers. Most other regional parks like Maplewood or Winona are also well-maintained by Norfolk Parks & Recreation.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Dog Parks Directory\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Norfolk\"}]}</script><header class=\"header header-visible  header-light\"><div class=\"header-container\"><div class=\"header-left\"><a class=\"logo\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Indoor Dog Park logo\" width=\"140\" height=\"40\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent;object-fit:contain;height:auto\" src=\"/images/logo/logo.png\"/></a></div><div class=\"header-center\"><nav class=\"header-nav\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\"><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/\">Browse Parks</a><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Discover <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/parks-with-bars\">Parks with Bars</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/training-facilities\">Training Facilities</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How It Works</a></div></div><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Locations <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-francisco\">San Francisco</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/los-angeles\">Los Angeles</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-diego\">San Diego</a><a class=\"header-dropd