at makes this dog facility special is its spacious, clean, safe. spacious indoor play areas Located in a safe area, This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (757) 857-5414. \",\"slug\":\"9-tails-pet-grooming-salon\",\"address\":\"1616 Meadow Lake Dr\",\"street\":\"1616 Meadow Lake Dr\",\"city\":\"Norfolk\",\"state\":\"VA\",\"zipCode\":\"23518\",\"full_address\":\"1616 Meadow Lake Dr, Norfolk, VA 23518, USA\",\"latitude\":36.8989435,\"longitude\":-76.2253856,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJ-xQXbz2XuokRlRV6CHvoDzA\",\"phone\":\"(757) 857-5414\",\"website\":\"\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.9,\"reviewCount\":44,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"Closed\",\"Tuesday\":\"8:30 AM – 5:30 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"8:30 AM – 5:30 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"8:30 AM – 5:30 PM\",\"Friday\":\"8:30 AM – 5:30 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"8:30 AM – 5:30 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"Closed\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":false,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJkW-KGEyXuokRNRvAS5KWK70\",\"name\":\"Bayview Pet Salon\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Bayview Pet Salon.  What makes this dog facility special is its clean, friendly, caring. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. clean and well-maintained facilities This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (757) 639-3004. \",\"slug\":\"bayview-pet-salon\",\"address\":\"1541 A E Bayview Blvd\",\"street\":\"1541 A E Bayview Blvd\",\"city\":\"Norfolk\",\"state\":\"VA\"